name: ListDataPoliciesRequest
description:
Request message for the ListDataPolicies method.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.bigquery.datapolicies.v1.ListDataPoliciesRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. Resource name of the project for which to list data policies. Format is projects/{project_number}/locations/{location_id}.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of data policies to return. Must be a value between 1 and 1000. If not set, defaults to 50.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: The nextPageToken value returned from a previous list request, if any. If not set, defaults to an empty string.

params.name: data.filter
params.description: Filters the data policies by policy tags that they are associated with. Currently filter only supports "policy_tag" based filtering and OR based predicates. Sample filter can be "policy_tag: 'projects/1/locations/us/taxonomies/2/policyTags/3'". You may use wildcard such as "policy_tag: 'projects/1/locations/us/taxonomies/2/*'".
